{"title":"妈妈的叮咛","authors":["刘芳"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈的叮咛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子！我告诉你："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你已不是妈妈个人的宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我已把你交给了毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让你跟着他学，跟着他"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子！让我跟你说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理只有一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是属于人民的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多了都是假的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子！我只能告诉你这一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其他我就不清楚了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可以鼓起勇气壮起胆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向毛主席学习，向工农学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子！谁的儿女谁不爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我得好好对你有个安排；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是为了我，而是为了你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们第二代。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我得指给你一个光明的未"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}